{"tid":748179,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"中國駐海參崴總領館警告：中國人勿帶走海灘石塊","createTime":"2018-07-19T04:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T09:55:33.000Z","uid":41404,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ac04eb4fe9985bd33114f3f2fa5e9f5f976feb6e","tid":748179,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:04:24.000Z","msg":"中國駐海參崴（Vladivostok）總領館，今日通過官方微信，提醒中國旅客到俄羅斯遠東海參崴的玻璃海灘遊玩時，不要帶走海灘上的玻璃石。<br />\n<br />\n繼續睇：<br />\n【海參崴遇「襲」】蘇聯酒樽堆填區變玻璃海灘 中國客愛打卡放閃（<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2uJ7H31）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2uJ7H31%EF%BC%89&d=5yHp%2FArRmvewwdqCqKTArB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=b093c1f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2uJ7H31）</a><br />\n總領館表示，據當地媒體日前報道，有中國遊客無視「禁止帶走玻璃石子」的警告字句，大量撿拾玻璃石並帶離，破壞了海灘環境，給當地居民造成困擾。總領館還發現，一些中方旅行社和導遊準備的宣傳中聲稱，遊客可從玻璃海灘帶走玻璃石；但事實上，這並不符合俄方規定。<br />\n總領館鄭重提醒：一、中方旅行社和導遊，切勿用可以撿拾玻璃石向遊客推銷玻璃海灘遊覽項目，務必提前提醒遊客在玻璃海灘遊玩時，不要帶走玻璃石；二、中國遊客在玻璃海灘遊玩要注意文明舉止，維護形象，以免發生不愉快事件，受到追究。<br />\n玻璃海灘目前面臨消亡危機，俄羅斯遠東聯邦大學教授波洛夫科與其團隊，去年對玻璃海灘上的500片玻璃進行研究後表示，再過20年這片「玻璃海灘」或將不復存在。波洛夫科指，玻璃海灘消失的主要原因有兩點：一是因為大自然的磨損，二則是人為原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180718/58456149\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180718%2F58456149&d=5yHp%2FArRmvewwdqCqKTArB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=3d67dff0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180718%2F58456149&h=20043314\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180718/58456149</a>"},{"pid":"bece1ad9216b9ea527f033d7e0440fe87f59686d","tid":748179,"uid":33907,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:08:23.000Z","msg":"打倒俄羅斯<br />\n收復海參崴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾時做到啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7b2511f415c22f01629399a3a5c5dfa24660fe","tid":748179,"uid":987,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:09:44.000Z","msg":"on9中國地方ge野點解唔拎得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd32a72427a75a39cea496d4c80ceab426c7fcd","tid":748179,"uid":57308,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:22:25.000Z","msg":"中國國土，寸土不讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾時拎返啊雜總大大"},{"pid":"01ca1eb0616aee4c54d2e97024bdcf25ad53382b","tid":748179,"uid":8048,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:23:58.000Z","msg":"遼撚號出咗去維權未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00eab036097c0d79f936e629500ed28f06d4e194","tid":748179,"uid":123738,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:28:22.000Z","msg":"支那國土，鐘意點就點啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又散布假消息<br />\n其實支那狗去到俄，應該周地痾屎，以示蟈力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96abec3f76d078fa0520114b021061d19534ebd0","tid":748179,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:31:09.000Z","msg":"蝗禍"},{"pid":"49132c78877da2522aaf79bb5d5c888b6ceb797c","tid":748179,"uid":131600,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:05:21.000Z","msg":"又話一點都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係有本事既 海參崴領事館就係俄羅斯開唔係中國開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09fb7e0058a1613fc3b9db665effec52a2e8edb9","tid":74